# Step quality gates (code steps)

> Extends slim `core-rules.mdc`. Full policy: `@.cursor/rules/core-rules-full.mdc`

## Before merge

| Gate | Threshold |
|------|-----------|
| Lint errors | 0 |
| TypeScript strict errors | 0 |
| Test coverage — lines / branches / functions | ≥ 80% / ≥ 75% / ≥ 85% |
| SAST (Critical / High) | 0 |
| Dependency CVEs (CVSS ≥ 9.0) | 0 |
| Secret scan | 0 |
| Cyclomatic complexity | ≤ 10 per function |
| Function length | ≤ 50 lines |

Naming: files kebab-case; classes PascalCase; functions camelCase; DB snake_case; env UPPER_SNAKE_CASE.

## Security & performance (summary)

- Auth on endpoints; authz at service layer
- Validate input at API boundary; parameterized queries only
- Secrets in env / secret manager; no PII in logs
- Paginate lists (default 20, max 100); no N+1; connection pooling
- Frontend: LCP < 2.5s, INP < 200ms, CLS < 0.1 (or product SLO)
